## Professional Profile

As a dedicated software engineer, I specialize in architecting and building performant web applications using modern JavaScript/TypeScript and Python ecosystems. My approach combines technical excellence with thoughtful system design, delivering solutions that are both robust and maintainable.

Key strengths:
- **Django** development for scalable backend systems and REST APIs
- Full-stack development with focus on React and Node.js ecosystems
- Strong advocate for type-safe development with TypeScript
- High-performance frontends using Vite build tool
- Passion for creating intuitive developer experiences through clean APIs and documentation
- Commitment to writing testable, scalable code with performance considerations
- Effective collaborator in cross-functional agile teams

